      • Map

        public Map(int levelOn)
        Loads level from level file using Levels.java. Beforehand, sets up defaults for parameters that can be overridden by Levels.java (minisize, name, etc).
        Parameters:
        levelOn - level to load (located in levels/level[levelOn].txt)

        public boolean removeComponent(int x,

      • getComponentsToTick

        public java.util.ArrayList<MapComponent> getComponentsToTick()
        Generates a sorted ArrayList of MapComponents to tick, sorted by component precedence (defined by the components). Note that does not update components with update prevented, or when their delay interval isn't up.
        Returns:
        the ArrayList of MapComponents
